WEBVTT

00:02.168 --> 00:03.870
<i>PREVIOUSLY, ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

00:03.870 --> 00:05.371
TAKE THE HANDCUFFS
OFF MY SON.

00:05.371 --> 00:07.173
GET OUT OF MY HOUSE.

00:07.173 --> 00:09.409
CANDACE, WHAT HAPPENED
TO MY GRANDBABY?

00:09.409 --> 00:11.211
I GAVE QUINCY THE MONEY.

00:11.211 --> 00:13.680
AND HE TOLD ME
THAT HE KILLED HIM.

00:13.680 --> 00:15.248
I WASN'T EVEN REALLY AWARE
YOU HAD A BOYFRIEND.

00:15.248 --> 00:16.950
[ CHUCKLES ]
HIS NAME IS QUINCY.

00:16.950 --> 00:18.284
DO YOU WANT TO COME BACK
FOR DINNER?

00:18.284 --> 00:19.853
ALL RIGHT.
I WANT TO HAVE SOME FUN.

00:19.853 --> 00:21.054
YOU WANT US TO TAKE CARE
OF HIM?

00:21.054 --> 00:23.590
I WANT HIM BROUGHT HERE
SO I CAN HANDLE HIM MYSELF.

00:23.590 --> 00:26.292
HOLD ON A SECOND.
LET ME EXPLAIN.

00:26.292 --> 00:27.961
YOU DON'T RECOGNIZE ME?

00:27.961 --> 00:29.195
WHY THE HELL
SHOULD I RECOGNIZE YOU?

00:29.195 --> 00:30.396
I'M YOUR SON.

00:33.266 --> 00:36.269
CELINE!

00:36.269 --> 00:39.072
CELINE, GET IN HERE NOW.
YES?

00:39.072 --> 00:41.908
YOU DID THIS?

00:41.908 --> 00:44.911
I DID WHAT, SIR?

00:44.911 --> 00:48.481
YOU HAD THAT KID WORKING
IN MY CAMPAIGN OFFICE.

00:48.481 --> 00:49.583
YOU DID THAT.

00:49.583 --> 00:51.818
THAT KID?

00:51.818 --> 00:53.419
YOU MEAN OUR SON?

00:53.419 --> 00:56.122
I DIDN'T DO THAT.

00:56.122 --> 00:58.258
THEN WHY THE HELL
IS HE IN MY OFFICE,

00:58.258 --> 01:00.293
AND WHY THE HELL
IS HE IN MY HOUSE?

01:00.293 --> 01:02.903
YOU SHOULD KNOW.

01:02.903 --> 01:04.638
HOW SHOULD I KNOW,
CELINE?

01:04.638 --> 01:07.473
BECAUSE YOU HAVE NEVER TALKED
TO HIM.

01:07.473 --> 01:09.475
EVER.

01:09.475 --> 01:11.512
HE SEES YOU, JIM.

01:11.512 --> 01:13.279
HE SEES
HOW WELL YOU'RE DOING.

01:13.279 --> 01:16.449
YOU HEARD HIM.
THAT'S NOT EASY FOR HIM.

01:16.449 --> 01:19.786
HOW DID HE KNOW
I WAS HIS FATHER?

01:25.759 --> 01:27.493
WHAT, ARE YOU STUCK
FOR AN ANSWER?

01:27.493 --> 01:29.162
HOW DID HE KNOW
I WAS HIS FATHER?

01:29.162 --> 01:32.833
LOOK AT HIM, JIM.

01:32.833 --> 01:34.501
DO YOU THINK
HE'S STUPID?

01:34.501 --> 01:36.469
DO YOU THINK
HE DOESN'T REALIZE

01:36.469 --> 01:38.438
THAT HE DOESN'T LOOK
ANYTHING LIKE HIS SIBLINGS?

01:38.438 --> 01:41.675
THAT STILL DOESN'T EXPLAIN
HOW HE KNEW I WAS HIS FATHER,

01:41.675 --> 01:43.209
DOES IT, CELINE?

01:43.209 --> 01:46.980
HE REMEMBERS YOU.

01:46.980 --> 01:49.382
HE REMEMBERS YOU HOLDING HIM
AS A LITTLE BOY.

01:49.382 --> 01:52.485
HE PUT IT ALL TOGETHER,
JIM.

01:55.989 --> 01:58.458
WHAT DOES HE WANT?

02:00.701 --> 02:02.503
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:02.503 --> 02:04.037
HE WANTS A FATHER.

02:04.037 --> 02:06.006
OH, COME ON.

02:06.006 --> 02:08.141
WHAT DOES HE WANT,
CELINE?

02:08.141 --> 02:09.810
HOW MUCH DOES HE WANT?

02:09.810 --> 02:12.245
HE WANTS YOUR TIME, JIM.

02:12.245 --> 02:13.914
REALLY?

02:15.882 --> 02:18.317
I'M NOT GIVING HIM
A DIME.

02:18.317 --> 02:21.387
NOT ONE THIN DIME.

02:21.387 --> 02:25.058
YOU THINK MY SON

02:25.058 --> 02:27.227
IS THE KIND OF PERSON THAT
WOULD EXTORT MONEY FROM YOU?!

02:27.227 --> 02:29.596
IT'S ALWAYS ABOUT MONEY,
CELINE.

02:29.596 --> 02:31.565
[ Chuckling ] GOD.

02:31.565 --> 02:36.036
YOU ARE A PATHETIC EXCUSE FOR
A HUMAN BEING, YOU KNOW THAT?

02:36.036 --> 02:38.539
THIS IS NOT ABOUT MONEY,
JIM.

02:38.539 --> 02:43.844
THIS IS ABOUT YOU BEING A FATHER
TO MY SON, TO OUR SON!

02:49.983 --> 02:52.252
YOU DON'T THINK IT'S THAT,
DO YOU?

02:52.252 --> 02:55.488
YOU DON'T KNOW ANYTHING
AT ALL.

02:55.488 --> 03:00.634
GOD, HOW CAN A HUMAN BEING BE
SO CLUELESS?!

03:00.634 --> 03:03.103
MY SON ‐‐

03:03.103 --> 03:05.438
THAT BOY THAT WE CREATED ‐‐

03:05.438 --> 03:06.773
HE'S FAIR.

03:06.773 --> 03:11.177
HE JUST WANTS WHAT'S FAIR,
JUST LIKE ME.

03:13.179 --> 03:15.348
I'M SORRY.
WHAT DID YOU SAY?

03:15.348 --> 03:17.383
FAIR?

03:17.383 --> 03:18.919
JUST LIKE YOU?

03:18.919 --> 03:21.387
YES.

03:21.387 --> 03:24.090
REALLY?
YES.

03:24.090 --> 03:26.326
JUST LIKE ME.

03:29.129 --> 03:32.165
I'VE NEVER DEMANDED
ANYTHING OF YOU.

03:32.165 --> 03:33.934
EVER.

03:33.934 --> 03:37.170
AND GOD KNOWS
I HAVE SO MUCH ON YOU.

03:37.170 --> 03:39.973
I'VE NEVER PUT YOU
IN A POSITION TO HURT YOU,

03:39.973 --> 03:41.975
NO MATTER HOW MUCH
YOU'VE HURT ME,

03:41.975 --> 03:43.844
AND ‐‐ AND YOU'VE HURT ME,
JIM.

03:43.844 --> 03:46.346
ALL I DO IS DO MY JOB.

03:46.346 --> 03:47.914
I WORK HERE.

03:47.914 --> 03:50.083
I CLEAN UP AFTER YOUR WIFE,
YOUR KIDS.

03:50.083 --> 03:51.918
FOR YEARS,
I'VE BEEN DOING IT.

03:51.918 --> 03:55.155
AND WHAT HAVE I ASKED OF YOU?
WHAT HAVE I EVER ASKED OF YOU?!

03:55.155 --> 03:56.890
NOT ONE THING.

04:02.168 --> 04:05.171
